
---

### `.gitignore` File

Create a file named `.gitignore` in your repository root and paste this:

```gitignore
# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor files
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# Logs
*.log

# Environment / secrets (never commit these)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Node / build artifacts (if you ever add any)
node_modules/
dist/
build/

# Temporary files
tmp/
temp/

# Don't commit real personal data
# (You can remove this line if you want)
personal-info.txt
